r centrally-acting alpha-2 agonists has not been established.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/9640/', '', 'Pemoline, Metamfetamine, Lisdexamfetamine, Solriamfetol, Caffeine, Dextroamphetamine, Armodafinil, Citicoline', 'Apraclonidine, Methazolamide, Neostigmine, Physostigmine, Acetylcholine, Diclofenamide, Bimatoprost, Travoprost, Acetazolamide, Brinzolamide, Brimonidine, More', 1767369485);
